{"tid":471877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉偷奶粉藥物值逾7萬　停職警被改控3項偷竊","createTime":"2017-11-17T16:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T11:02:40.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0a36da6838725d09d2ce13f694481112bae134","tid":471877,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"因疑捲入欺詐案和多宗爆竊案而遭停職受查的重案組男警，9月中涉嫌在屯門一幢工業大廈內企圖偷走一輛載有120罐奶粉的手推車，總值2.5萬港元，原被控一項企圖盜竊罪，案件今(17日)在屯門法院再訊。控方把被告被控的企圖盜竊罪，修改為偷竊罪，另新增兩項偷竊罪。 <br />\n<br />\n辯方要求暫毋須答辯，讓辯方索取法律意見和文件，裁判官遂把案件押後至12月22日再訊，期間被告繼續還押。 <br />\n<br />\n報稱公務員的被告陳曉健現被控於本年9月18日，在屯門工業中心B座地下升降機大堂偷取120罐奶粉，總值2.5萬港元。被告亦被控在同月25日，在屯門工業中心B座2樓偷取144罐奶粉，總值2.9萬多港元，以及在旺角廣東道一大廈，偷取一箱藥物，價值1.9萬多港元。三項合共逾7萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171117/mobile/bkn-20171117133933793-1117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171117%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171117133933793-1117_00822_001.html&d=9hIivRAVChbBZy%2BCr3HrpcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=ac033a44\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171117/mobile/bkn-20171117133933793-1117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4e85efe031f7e8bdc4dc981b88390674463f48d0","tid":471877,"uid":124007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"咁撚鍾意飲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350fa96c8a648e043cdfa96f090d672df64f8c35","tid":471877,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"嗱黑警呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data